<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hi">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Sugar Saar – Diabetes से आज़ादी</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Yatra+One&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700;900&family=Noto+Sans+Devanagari:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --saffron: #FF6B00;
    --deep-green: #1A4D2E;
    --gold: #D4A017;
    --cream: #FFF8ED;
    --brown: #5C2E00;
    --red: #C0392B;
    --light-green: #E8F5E9;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Poppins', 'Noto Sans Devanagari', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: #1a1a1a;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1A4D2E 0%, #0d2e1a 60%, #2d1a00 100%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 20px 80px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.03'%3E%3Ccircle cx='30' cy='30' r='4'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), #f5c842);
    color: var(--brown);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 8px 20px;
    border-radius: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    animation: fadeDown 0.8s ease both;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Yatra One', cursive;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 6.5rem);
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    text-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    animation: fadeDown 0.9s 0.1s ease both;
  }

  .hero h1 span { color: var(--gold); }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.4rem);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    font-weight: 300;
    animation: fadeDown 1s 0.2s ease both;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2.5vw, 1.1rem);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    animation: fadeDown 1s 0.3s ease both;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--saffron), #e84e00);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 18px 50px;
    border-radius: 60px;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(255,107,0,0.5);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    animation: fadeUp 1s 0.4s ease both;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
  }

  .hero-cta:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.03);
    box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(255,107,0,0.6);
  }

  .hero-note {
    margin-top: 18px;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    animation: fadeUp 1s 0.5s ease both;
  }

  .scroll-indicator {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 28px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    animation: bounce 2s infinite;
  }

  .scroll-indicator::after {
    content: '↓';
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  /* floating leaves */
  .leaf {
    position: absolute;
    width: 60px; opacity: 0.07;
    animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .leaf:nth-child(1)  { top: 10%; left: 5%;  animation-delay: 0s; }
  .leaf:nth-child(2)  { top: 30%; right: 8%; animation-delay: 2s; }
  .leaf:nth-child(3)  { bottom: 20%; left: 3%; animation-delay: 4s; }
  .leaf:nth-child(4)  { bottom: 10%; right: 5%; animation-delay: 1s; }

  /* ── STRIP ── */
  .strip {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--saffron), var(--gold), var(--saffron));
    padding: 14px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .strip-inner {
    display: inline-block;
    white-space: nowrap;
    animation: marquee 18s linear infinite;
  }

  /* ── SECTION SHARED ── */
  section { padding: 80px 20px; }

  .container { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--saffron);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Yatra One', cursive;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    color: var(--deep-green);
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .section-title span { color: var(--saffron); }

  .section-body {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: #444;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  /* ── ORIGIN STORY ── */
  .origin {
    background: #fff;
  }

  .origin-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .year-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 140px; height: 140px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--deep-green), #0d2e1a);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-family: 'Yatra One', cursive;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(26,77,46,0.35);
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    flex-direction: column;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .year-badge small { font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }

  .origin-visual {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 20px;
  }

  .flag-stripe {
    display: flex;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    width: 100%;
    height: 18px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }

  .flag-stripe div { flex: 1; }
  .flag-saffron { background: #FF9933; }
  .flag-white   { background: #fff; border-top: 1px solid #eee; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
  .flag-green   { background: #138808; }

  .quote-box {
    background: var(--light-green);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--deep-green);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--brown);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  /* ── INGREDIENTS ── */
  .ingredients {
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #1A4D2E 0%, #0d3320 100%);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .ingredients .section-title { color: #fff; }
  .ingredients .section-label { color: var(--gold); }

  .herb-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .herb-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s, background 0.3s;
    backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
  }

  .herb-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  }

  .herb-icon { font-size: 2.4rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }

  .herb-name {
    font-family: 'Yatra One', cursive;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .herb-desc { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* ── HOW IT WORKS ── */
  .how {
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    margin-top: 50px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .steps::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 32px;
    top: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--saffron), var(--deep-green));
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 30px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 0 0 44px 0;
  }

  .step-num {
    min-width: 64px; height: 64px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--saffron), #e84e00);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255,107,0,0.4);
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--deep-green);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .step-content p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.7; }

  /* ── SOCIAL PROOF ── */
  .proof {
    background: #fff;
  }

  .trust-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 50px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin: 40px 0;
  }

  .trust-item {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .trust-num {
    font-family: 'Yatra One', cursive;
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--saffron);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .trust-label { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #777; margin-top: 4px; }

  .testimonials {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .tcard {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    border: 1px solid #f0e6d3;
    position: relative;
  }

  .tcard::before {
    content: '"';
    position: absolute;
    top: 12px; left: 20px;
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.3;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .tcard-text {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: #444;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    padding-top: 14px;
  }

  .tcard-author {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }

  .tcard-avatar {
    width: 44px; height: 44px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--deep-green), var(--saffron));
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .tcard-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #222; }
  .tcard-loc  { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #888; }

  .stars { color: var(--gold); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 2px; }

  /* ── CELEBRITIES / TRUST ── */
  .celeb-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF3E0, #FFF8ED);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 70px 20px;
  }

  .celeb-section .section-title { text-align: center; }
  .celeb-section .section-label { text-align: center; }

  .celeb-badges {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 36px;
  }

  .celeb-badge {
    background: #fff;
    border: 2px solid var(--gold);
    color: var(--brown);
    padding: 10px 22px;
    border-radius: 40px;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(212,160,23,0.15);
  }

  /* ── CTA SECTION ── */
  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--saffron) 0%, #c94a00 100%);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 90px 20px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='80' height='80' viewBox='0 0 80 80' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.04'%3E%3Cpath d='M0 0h80v80H0z'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='40' cy='40' r='30'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Yatra One', cursive;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .cta-phone {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--saffron);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    padding: 20px 48px;
    border-radius: 60px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
    position: relative;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .cta-phone:hover { transform: scale(1.04); }
  .cta-phone .phone-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; animation: ring 1.5s infinite; }

  .cta-note {
    margin-top: 22px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* ── WHY NOT MEDICAL STORE ── */
  .exclusive {
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .exclusive-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--deep-green), #1a3d24);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 50px 40px;
    color: #fff;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 50px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .exclusive-box h2 {
    font-family: 'Yatra One', cursive;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .exclusive-box p { font-size: 0.97rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); line-height: 1.8; }

  .exclusive-points {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;
  }

  .exc-point {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px;
  }

  .exc-icon {
    min-width: 40px; height: 40px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .exc-text strong { display: block; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .exc-text span   { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); }

  /* ── FAQ ── */
  .faq { background: #fff; }

  .faq-list { margin-top: 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }

  .faq-item {
    border: 1px solid #e8dcc8;
    border-radius: 14px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .faq-q {
    width: 100%; text-align: left;
    background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--deep-green);
    font-family: 'Poppins', 'Noto Sans Devanagari', sans-serif;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .faq-q:hover { background: var(--cream); }
  .faq-arrow { font-size: 1.2rem; transition: transform 0.3s; color: var(--saffron); }
  .faq-item.open .faq-arrow { transform: rotate(180deg); }

  .faq-a {
    max-height: 0; overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s ease, padding 0.3s;
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.75;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .faq-item.open .faq-a { max-height: 300px; padding: 0 24px 20px; }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: #0d1f10;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  footer strong { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ── STICKY CTA BAR ── */
  .sticky-bar {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--deep-green), #1a3d24);
    padding: 14px 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
    z-index: 999;
    box-shadow: 0 -4px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .sticky-text {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .sticky-text span { color: var(--gold); }

  .sticky-btn {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--saffron), #e84e00);
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding: 12px 30px;
    border-radius: 40px;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(255,107,0,0.45);
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .sticky-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.04); }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  @keyframes fadeDown {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-24px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
    50%       { transform: translateY(-18px) rotate(10deg); }
  }

  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    50%       { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(8px); }
  }

  @keyframes ring {
    0%, 100% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    20%       { transform: rotate(-15deg); }
    40%       { transform: rotate(15deg); }
    60%       { transform: rotate(-10deg); }
    80%       { transform: rotate(10deg); }
  }

  @keyframes marquee {
    from { transform: translateX(100vw); }
    to   { transform: translateX(-100%); }
  }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .origin-grid     { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 30px; }
    .exclusive-box   { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 36px 24px; }
    .steps::before   { left: 28px; }
    .step-num        { min-width: 56px; height: 56px; font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .sticky-bar      { gap: 10px; padding: 12px 14px; }
    .sticky-text     { font-size: 0.8rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <!-- floating leaves SVG -->
  <svg class="leaf" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none"><ellipse cx="50" cy="50" rx="30" ry="48" fill="#4CAF50" transform="rotate(30 50 50)"/></svg>
  <svg class="leaf" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none"><ellipse cx="50" cy="50" rx="26" ry="42" fill="#81C784" transform="rotate(-20 50 50)"/></svg>
  <svg class="leaf" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none"><ellipse cx="50" cy="50" rx="28" ry="45" fill="#66BB6A" transform="rotate(15 50 50)"/></svg>
  <svg class="leaf" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none"><ellipse cx="50" cy="50" rx="24" ry="40" fill="#4CAF50" transform="rotate(-35 50 50)"/></svg>

  <div class="hero-badge">🌿 1947 से आजमाया हुआ — 78 साल का विश्वास</div>
  <h1>Sugar <span>Saar</span></h1>
  <div class="hero-sub">Diabetes से मिलेगी असली आज़ादी — पहले Dose से ही</div>
  <div class="hero-tagline">7 दुर्लभ जड़ी-बूटियों का वह Formula जो Medical Industry छुपाना चाहती है</div>
  <a href="tel:+911234567890" class="hero-cta">📞 अभी Call करें — FREE Consultation</a>
  <div class="hero-note">⚡ सीधा Ashram से आपके घर तक · Medical Store पर उपलब्ध नहीं</div>

  <div class="scroll-indicator">नीचे देखें</div>
</section>

<!-- TICKER -->
<div class="strip">
  <span class="strip-inner">
    ✅ 78 साल पुराना Formula &nbsp;|&nbsp; 🌿 100% Natural Herbs &nbsp;|&nbsp; ⚡ पहले Dose से असर &nbsp;|&nbsp; 🏠 घर पर Delivery &nbsp;|&nbsp; 📞 Free Expert Consultation &nbsp;|&nbsp; ✅ Doctors, Celebrities & Politicians का भरोसा &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
    ✅ 78 साल पुराना Formula &nbsp;|&nbsp; 🌿 100% Natural Herbs &nbsp;|&nbsp; ⚡ पहले Dose से असर &nbsp;|&nbsp; 🏠 घर पर Delivery &nbsp;|&nbsp; 📞 Free Expert Consultation &nbsp;|&nbsp; ✅ Doctors, Celebrities & Politicians का भरोसा
  </span>
</div>

<!-- ORIGIN STORY -->
<section class="origin">
  <div class="container">
